readable.content: A person belted into a bungee-jumping ride in midair . A person is flipping upside down while attached to some bungee cords . A person is suspended by wires and poles against a blue sky . A person wearing a white shirt and blue shorts with cables attached to him . A shoeless strapped in individual jumping with rubber bands attached is airborne .
